OL,4,Cfollowing dispute
OL,6,FTwo men have been jailed for life
OL,7,Fafter "mercilessly" murdering their
OL,8,Fneighbour following a confrontation in
OL,9,FYeovil.
OL,11,FMark Sothcott and Martin Carty were
OL,12,Fconvicted of murdering 68-year-old
OL,13,FFranklin Ingram following a three-week
OL,14,Ftrial in December.
OL,16,FMr Ingram was killed following a
OL,17,Fconfrontation with the pair at Carty's
OL,18,Fflat in Raglan Terrace shortly after
OL,19,F11pm on 22 June 2024.
