OL,6,FCarty waited 18 hours before calling
OL,7,Femergency services, at which point he
OL,8,Ffalsely claimed to have found Mr
OL,9,FIngram dead on a sofa.
OL,11,FParamedics informed police of the
OL,12,Fdeath due to the seriousness of Mr
OL,13,FIngram's injuries, and Carty was later
OL,14,Farrested.
OL,16,FSothcott, of Stiby Road, was arrested
OL,17,Fon 24 June after comments he made to
OL,18,Fmembers of the public were reported to
OL,19,Fpolice.
