OL,6,F'It wasn't just me who loved Franklin'
OL,7,F- victim's partner
OL,9,FIn a prepared statement, Mr Ingram's
OL,10,Fcivil partner Vania Leprieult said his
OL,11,Fdeath had had a "massive effect on me
OL,12,Fand my family and friends".
OL,14,F"It wasn't just me who loved Franklin;
OL,15,Fwe have many friends together here in
OL,16,FFrance," she said.
OL,18,F"The people here say they have never
OL,19,Fseen two people love each other so
OL,20,Fmuch; we fit each other so well.
