OL,6,F"We were like two kids, playing all
OL,7,Fthe time. We shared a lot of humour
OL,8,Ftogether. That is all gone now."
OL,10,FHis Honour Judge Peter Blair described
OL,11,FMr Ingram's death as an "utterly
OL,12,Fneedless loss of life will have a
OL,13,Flasting effect on those that love him".
OL,15,FHe stated Carty "mercilessly" attacked
OL,16,FMr Ingram and inflicted the fatal
OL,17,Fblow, and that Sothcott encouraged it.
