OL,3,CMen jailed for murdering neighbour
OL,4,Cfollowing dispute
OL,6,FCarty, 56, received a life sentence at
OL,7,FBristol Crown Court on Friday 14
OL,8,FFebruary. He will serve a minimum of
OL,9,F13 years.
OL,11,FA life sentence was handed to Sothcott
OL,12,Fat a separate hearing held on Friday
OL,13,F23 January, where the 56-year-old was
OL,14,Ftold he would serve a minimum of eight
OL,15,Fyears.
